				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">There's even less aggro on Shock of Fiery Blades, but that is not a viable solution to the issue at hand. 
<br />

<br />
Namely: there is no DPS benefit to having/using Star Strike/A:Nova Strike over BoJ.
<br />

<br />
Actually, there's a Penalty. Because they are lvl70 spells, you not only need the spell, but updated focus to fully work on them. Whereas, the lvl66 bolt spell works just fine with old focuses (since anyone who has the ancient, surely has at least high end PoP or GoD focus which cap 67/68).<br />_________________<br />Master Elementalist Sebboh Nivlac
<br />
