				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I already have looked at the known "through 70" effects. It doesn't change the results. 
<br />

<br />
Even if there were a 30% mana focus (20% is the best in the spell data), Star Strike for a Spec:Conj mage is still worse than BoJ for a Spec:Evoc mage in both DPS and mana efficiency. A:NS is barely 1% better than BoJ in mana efficiency, significantly worse in DPS, and only for a Spec:Conj mage.
<br />

