				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Regarding the 2nd Ancient we get then whilst I would prefer to see an Ancient Pet or Ancient Burnout type spell another option is to actually provide an upgrade to the Elemental Siphon line we got in GoD (the current spells are not upgrades imo).
<br />

<br />
The lvl 70 version of this spell would change aswell so that it sits between GoD version and OoW Ancient. I think both these spells would be semi useful if they changed to the following:
<br />

<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Code:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="code">
<br />
Spell&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Pet Dmg&nbsp; &nbsp; Mana regen&nbsp; &nbsp; Duration
<br />
Siphon&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1200&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;5&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;6 min
<br />
Simulcrum&nbsp; &nbsp; 1500&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;7&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;7.5 min
<br />
Spike&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2000&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 10&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 10 min
<br />
</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />

<br />
Drop the rune component all together as I think its useless to have mana regen, what we really want from these spells, tied to a rune. The damage done to the pet using the above figures is constant in per minute terms.
<br />

<br />
I'd actually want to loot the 2nd Ancient spell if it got changed to this (and the Lvl 70 version if I couldn't get Ancient easily).<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=342751" target="_blank" class="postlink">Kirium</a>
